# Auto-load the demo's gitignored .env into any shell that enters this repo, so
# the legis / wardline MCP servers launched from here inherit LEGIS_OPERATOR_KEY,
# LEGIS_WARDLINE_ARTIFACT_KEY, LEGIS_HMAC_KEY (and the WARDLINE_* keys) — which is
# what makes `legis doctor` read clean out of the box.
#
# Requires direnv (https://direnv.net): run `direnv allow` once after `make setup`.
# WITHOUT direnv, source .env manually before launching the agent (see README):
#   set -a; . ./.env; set +a
#
# Secrets stay in .env (gitignored, 0600); this file is committed and contains none.
dotenv
